{"tid":1913383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良：中共今次一定派鬼參選𠝹票！但不要捉鬼互相攻擊！","createTime":"2020-03-06T17:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T06:22:52.000Z","uid":219007,"like":34,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"06c0223e00adf94eca63b2c5458f3cb8adb05c82","tid":1913383,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NSooq2LJO9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNSooq2LJO9g&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=af161992\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NSooq2LJO9g</a><br />\n01:27:00<br />\n<br />\n劉細良x 范國威：<br />\n<br />\n今次好多人都準備選立法會<br />\n係好需要初選同協調 <br />\n如果冇所謂，大家有權利去參選<br />\n但選民都有理智去同權利選擇<br />\n去到呢一刻，香港選民已經非常成熟<br />\n<br />\n中共今次一定派鬼扮演非建制派參選<br />\n但係最終決定權係選民度，我哋無需要為咗邊個參選而互相攻擊，千祈唔好<br />\n我哋要延續不分化不切割的精神<br />\n最終由選民決定誰人做立法會議員<br />\n而最後關頭嘅標準就係投俾最有機會當選嘅候選人<br />\n集中佢嘅選票<br />\n而呢樣嘢連登仔可能發揮佢嘅作用幫手計票<br />\n搵出最有機會當選嘅候選人<br />\n<br />\n因為今次未必有協調機制，亦都未必做到初選。"},{"pid":"6101e3feaaccee77ae1ca4dad099e068ebdedb93","tid":1913383,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果冇，冇所謂</span>"},{"pid":"0b8bd3a7561d9beb7be3261cf4929c84d64e4819","tid":1913383,"uid":201464,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:38:19.000Z","msg":"分化夠未"},{"pid":"e99ef54133a5f300e4fe7683e6ee0b1eca7a2186","tid":1913383,"uid":31841,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"捉鬼大師又黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次又屈邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a882df1625ca2e231898950755f5b2cbba426f2","tid":1913383,"uid":35348,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:49:51.000Z","msg":"鬼=白頭佬 黃碧雲"},{"pid":"3a723f23407174e7ad9fcd869a0ead32365d3068","tid":1913383,"uid":35104,"like":7,"dislike":1,"sc